|access-date=2020-07-07|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028110620/https://www.techannouncement.in/tech-news/google-plus-for-g-suite-gone-rebranded-as-google-currents/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，為[[G_Suite|G Suite系列]]产品之一<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.slashgear.com/google-currents-resurrected-as-g-suites-google-replacement-10572755/ |title=Google Currents resurrected as G Suite’s Google+ replacement |author=Torres, JC |website=SlashGear.com |access-date=2019-09-04 |archive-date=2020-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818072109/https://www.slashgear.com/google-currents-resurrected-as-g-suites-google-replacement-10572755/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

